{"tid":35630,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一秒清除電腦系統淤塞的所有垃圾！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2016-12-12T08:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T17:30:41.000Z","uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7eec725dcb9311e48e25aa12515741624f9df368","tid":35630,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"是否注意到你的電腦系統磁盤的可用空間正在一天天在減少呢？是不是動作一天比一天遲緩呢？<br />\n在Windows在安裝和使用過程中都會產生相當多的垃圾文件，包括臨時文件（如：*.tmp、*._mp）日誌文件（*.log）、臨時幫助文件（*.gid）、磁盤檢查文件（*.chk）、臨時備份文件（如：*.old、*.bak）以及其他臨時文件。特別是如果一段時間不清理IE的臨時文件夾「Temporary Internet Files」，其中的緩存文件有時會佔用上百MB的磁盤空間。這些LJ文件不僅僅浪費了寶貴的磁盤空間，嚴重時還會使系統運行慢如蝸牛。現在就讓我們一起來快速清除系統垃圾吧！！<br />\n下面是步驟很簡單就兩步！<br />\n打開「記事本」，把下面的字複製進去，點「另存為」，把文件名定為「清除系統垃圾.bat」就完成，記住後副檔名一定要是.bat，好ok了！你的垃圾清除器就這樣製作成功了！雙擊它就能很快地清理垃圾文件，大約一分鐘不到。 <br />\n複製下面的字：<br />\n<br />\n@echo off <br />\necho 正在清除系統垃圾文件，請稍等...... <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.tmp <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*._mp <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.log <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.gid <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.chk <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.old <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%recycled*.* <br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%*.bak <br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%prefetch*.* <br />\nrd /s /q %windir%temp &amp; md %windir%temp<br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%cookies*.* <br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%recent*.* <br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%Local SettingsTemporary Internet Files*.*&quot; <br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%Local SettingsTemp*.*&quot; <br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%recent*.*&quot; <br />\necho 清除系統垃圾完成！ <br />\necho. &amp; pause<br />\n<br />\n複製上面的字~~~以後只要雙擊運行該文件，當屏幕提示「清除系統垃圾完成！就還你一個「苗條」的系統了！！到時候再看看你的電腦，是不是急速如飛呢？"},{"pid":"155b1bbe5327d7a5ad075323b4cb85d599b11f67","tid":35630,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx ,部電腦依家好快"},{"pid":"19c88a9939cbe844648238f1856b8ed2cb731254","tid":35630,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:11:26.000Z","msg":"thx 樓主<br />\n真係得<br />\n而家部機勁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aa2008f0469d3671393318bff3ada98dc4be70","tid":35630,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"威力加強版呢"},{"pid":"e90f1337a2d2b3fbbb6a38239f83d5a01d38173b","tid":35630,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>威力加強版呢</blockquote><br />\n請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de39d12c7f10b0f8aa0f1708a2087785822811ba","tid":35630,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"快左20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8f8c4947559cfbefe1a7d89f1000d5a33b7ebd","tid":35630,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d8417fea92dc95d790a1d4916d1df7620c3f7f97","tid":35630,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>威力加強版呢</blockquote><br />\n請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個版本del嗰少少嘢同女人去整容差唔多，小修小補<br />\n<br />\n加強版就唔同，用咗之後部電腦同新嘅一樣，同初生bb一樣，用上手順到無人有<br />\n<br />\n支持貼出嚟，益街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d20dafc0e218d6e73ab5e1fe202d5fc90177ea","tid":35630,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"清爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6963abe9672703899f898001e0c51b357cdf6fd7","tid":35630,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>威力加強版呢</blockquote><br />\n請指教<img src=